reviews.text: Stay was good , room very good . Staff good but a duplicate booking has still to be refunded for night if 16 June 2019. I spoke to staff three times personally at check in and again check out and on return three weeks later at reception . I was assured all three times that the double payment would be refunded. Another 3 weeks at home and no refund or response at all from the numerous emails I have sent n copies of double payment. It’s HKG$1127.50 please refund to me .

Super friendly staff! They let us check in early as we were with young children and just got off a long flight. Indoor & outdoor pool are great! Room were clean and there are dining options within the hotel premises.

Great location and wide range of restaurants. Very convenient to the airport as we have an 9am departure. 
At 1.30am there was a loud commotion near our room with crying and shouting. After this was on going for a few minutes, I tried to ring front desk, concierge and operator. There were no pickup, I did not let each to ring very long and eventually gave it. Each have more than 3 rings. 
I don't like this if a BIG emergency was at hand!!!
The walls/insulation was very poor. Can head adjoining tv, and toilet use.
There are no alternative to another airport hotel that I know of, so may have to revisit again!

Well, this hotel is at the airport so very convenient. 
It is an awesome place to stay. Good Breakfast display, WiFi is provided, great laundry service, big gym, spa facilities, rooms are spacious. Many rooms have airport view so it's great. Room service is quick. It is a very good hotel with variety of facilities.
The staff are very professional, the restaurant has great food. The rooms are modern an well kept, also a nice view from my room. The spa area is very relaxing an dazzling at night.
